comments.body: This file is copied literally from Project Wycheproof (https://github.com/google/wycheproof), specifically https://github.com/google/wycheproof/blob/master/testvectors_v1/ecdsa_secp256k1_sha256_bitcoin_test.json. If there are typos in it, they should be fixed there first.

This file is a copy of https://github.com/google/wycheproof/blob/master/testvectors_v1/ecdsa_secp256k1_sha256_bitcoin_test.json . I don't think we want to touch it here. Please report upstream instead.
